studio.hypertext.atproto Kotlin Multiplatform library
Copyright 2026 Hypertext Studio

This library is published to Maven Central as the
`studio.hypertext.atproto:*` artifact family. The source lives in the
`shared/atproto-*` modules of the LogDate monorepo today and is scheduled
for extraction into a dedicated repository.

This product includes software developed at Hypertext Studio
(https://hypertext.studio).

It implements primitives of the AT Protocol as defined at
https://atproto.com.
